long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bring the adorable energy of Pikachu to your new tab! This Chrome extension adds a touch of Pokémon magic with a lively Pikachu wallpaper.

The Pokemon Pikachu live wallpaper extension lights up your browser with everyone’s favorite Electric-type Pokémon. With a clean, minimalist design, this extension combines fun visuals with essential browsing features.

Search the web easily using the Google search bar, organize shortcuts to favorite sites, and stay on top of the time with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring the beloved Pikachu
Google Search Bar for quick browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for easy access
Clock-Date display to stay organized

Enjoy a spark of Pokémon joy every time you open a tab with Pikachu! Discover more themes at Gameograf.com for even more fun options.
